===Noun===
# "[[separable]] [[verb]]," a type of Chinese verb which consists of two parts.  The two parts can go together, or other words can be placed in between the two parts.  For example: [[睡覺]] (to sleep) vs. [[睡]][[午|<font color="green">'''午'''</font>]][[覺]] (take a noon nap).

